134);">claims@tower.co.nz</span></a></span><span style=3D"font-size: =
11pt; font-family: Calibri, =
sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></div></div><div><div style=3D"margin: =
0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">As you do not yet have a motor claim with =
Tower from this event =E2=80=93 you can also send any motor reports to<a =
